description.en:
What is DecentralFree(FREELA)?

DecentralFree is a revolutionary contribution protocol that facilitates seamless collaboration and project completion across borders. DecentralFree leverages decentralized multichain technology to accelerate project delivery through token-funded micro-tasks. With DecentralFree, you can turn your ideas into reality without the hassle of managing complex task delegation or recruiting talent. DecentralFree's micro-task system enables flexible, decentralized task completion, with multiple contributors and price-setting. Project managers can select submissions based on quality and chronology, ensuring fair and efficient task completion.
